Body cylindrical, large sized, sometimes smaller (
7.9 mm
). Body black or dark brown, except elytra yellowish, sometimes surface along medial suture whitish. Legs, maxillary and labial palpi entirely brown. Antennae dark brown, except scape black, apical 1/3 of last antennomere yellowish.
